v3 Changelog:
Disco edited
war zone edited
texture overhaul


This v3 is a full release - it should be fine, however if there are problems, please report them.

Feel free to add on steam: mrburns4


***32 Players***
***22 T Spawn points***
***10 CT Spawn points***

***I permit anyone to use any part of this map, provided I remain credited AND the texture stating what area it is remains intact in whole***

Features: Mr Wolf, Bulldogs, Musical Chairs, Red light Green light, olympics(shotput, long jump, bhop, race, race of death) skate, nade war, war zone, dark room, maze, disco, pool, trivia zone, obstacle course, game zone

there are some things unusable currently that i will make use of in v4. This is the 3rd release as i have had a few problems along the way, hopefully i have nailed it this time.

***Missing textures now added***
